  "local_port": 44690,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I apply for commercial gas connection in Bangalore?",
  "response": "Applying for a commercial gas connection in Bangalore involves several steps. Here\u2019s a general guide to help you:\n\n### 1. Choose Gas Provider\nResearch and choose a gas provider suitable for your commercial needs. Some popular providers in Bangalore include:\n- Bharat Gas\n- Indane Gas\n- HP Gas\n\n### 2. Visit Provider\u2019s Website or Office\nYou can visit the official website of the chosen gas provider to collect information regarding the application process. Alternatively, you may visit their local office for assistance.\n\n### 3. Documents Required\nPrepare the necessary documents for the application. Common documents required include:\n- Business registration certificate\n- Proof of identity (PAN card, Aadhar card, passport, etc.)\n- Proof of address (electricity bill, water bill, rental agreement, etc.)\n- No Objection Certificate (NOC) from the landlord (if applicable)\n- Passport-sized photographs\n\n### 4. Application Process\nFollow these steps to apply:\n\n#### Online Application\n- Visit the gas provider\u2019s website.\n- Navigate to the commercial connection section.\n- Fill in the required details.\n- Upload scanned copies of the necessary documents.\n- Submit the application form.\n\n#### Offline Application\n- Visit the local gas provider\u2019s office.\n- Collect the application form for a commercial connection.\n- Fill out the form with accurate details.\n- Attach photocopies of the required documents.\n- Submit the completed form to the office.\n\n### 5. Pay Fees\nOnce the application is submitted, you may be required to pay certain fees such as:\n- Security deposit\n- Installation charges\n- Cost of equipment (cylinders, regulators, etc.)\n\n### 6. Verification and Installation\n- After submission, the gas provider will verify the submitted documents.\n- A site inspection might be conducted to ensure proper safety measures.\n- Upon approval, the installation process will be scheduled.\n- The provider will install the necessary equipment for the commercial gas connection.\n\n### 7. Activation\nOnce the installation is complete, the commercial gas connection will be activated, and you may start using it for your business operations.\n\n### Contacting Customer Support\nFor specific queries, contacting the customer support of the chosen gas provider will be helpful. They can provide detailed guidance tailored to your needs.\n\n### Tips\n- Ensure all details filled in the application form are accurate.\n- Keep copies of all submitted documents for future reference.\n- Adhere to safety regulations and guidelines provided by the gas provider.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to successfully apply for a commercial gas connection in Bangalore.",
